title: Winamp Pro v1.4.15
description:
Play, manage and sync music from your Mac or PC to your Android device. 

Winamp Pro offers a complete music management solution (2.1 OS & above) featuring wireless desktop sync (Winamp Media Player required), iTunes import, & access to thousands of internet radio stations with SHOUTcast.

Pro Features

* 10-band graphic equalizer
* Customizable home screen
* Browse by Folder
* Crossfade
* Gapless playback
* Support for FLAC playback in Folders View (lossless audio playback)
* Replay Gain
* Personalized station recommendations
* Play any streaming audio URL (supported formats only)
* No ads

What's New: (Updated: October 14, 2013)

New in Winamp 1.4.15
* Fixed: Crash that may occur when starting Winamp and turning on Lyrics feature with no network connectivity.
